  "texts": [
    "Ding et al.",
    "developed a deep learning algorithm that interprets PET of the brain for the early prediction of AD.",
    "Their model showed a specificity and sensitivity of 82% and 100%, respectively.",
    "This model can predict AD, on average, 75.8 months before its diagnosis, with an AUROC of 0.98 (Ding et al. 2019).",
    "Recently, Agbavor and Liang developed an end-to-end AI-powered system for the detection of AD as well as to predict the severity of the disease from raw voice recordings (Agbavor and Liang 2022)."
  ],
